DSET ^les_03-02.atm
OPTIONS BIG_ENDIAN
OPTIONS template
TITLE les_03-02.atm
UNDEF 1.0e+37
XDEF        64 LINEAR 1 1
YDEF        72 LINEAR 1 1
ZDEF        37 LINEAR 1 1
TDEF       1 LINEAR 00:00Z00JAN0001 1YR
VARS    5
tmpa3d      37 99 Temperature perturbation (K)
absg3d      37 99 Absorption coefficient perturbation (/m)
extp3d      37 99 Extinction coefficient (/m)
omgp3d      37 99 Single scattering albedo
apfp3d      37 99 Phase function specification parameter
ENDVARS
